            "text": "Why Buy From Golden West Games",
            "heading_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "richtext-1": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>For over 75 years, Golden West Games has been Western Washington's trusted destination for premium billiard tables and accessories. Unlike big-box retailers, every table in our collection has been hand-selected, inspected, and can be seen in person at our 5,000 sq. ft. showroom.</p><p>We don't just sell tables — we deliver them, install them, and stand behind them. Our team of experienced technicians handles everything from white-glove delivery to professional leveling, felt installation, and ongoing service.</p>"
          }
        },
        "button-1": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "style": "solid",
            "text": "Visit Our Showroom",
            "background": "#c5a258",
            "text_color": "#1a1a1a"
          }
        }
