    "testimonials": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial-1": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Golden West delivered and installed our Presidential pool table flawlessly. The team was professional, on time, and the table plays beautifully. Couldn't be happier with the experience.</p>",
            "author": "— Satisfied Customer",
            "logo_max_width": 140,
            "logo_mobile_max_width": 100
          }
        },
        "testimonial-2": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We visited the showroom and were blown away by the selection. Being able to see and feel the tables in person made all the difference. The staff really knows their stuff.</p>",
            "author": "— Satisfied Customer",
            "logo_max_width": 140,
            "logo_mobile_max_width": 100
          }
        },
        "testimonial-3": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>After 10 years, our Golden West table still looks and plays like new. When we needed the felt replaced, their service team came out and had it done in no time. That's the kind of after-sale support you can't get online.</p>",
            "author": "— Satisfied Customer",
            "logo_max_width": 140,
            "logo_mobile_max_width": 100
          }
        }
