            "text": "Our Story",
            "heading_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "richtext-2": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Golden West Games was founded in 1947 in the heart of Western Washington with a simple mission: bring the finest billiard tables and game room furnishings to the Pacific Northwest.</p><p>What started as a small family-run shop has grown into the region's largest billiard showroom — but our values haven't changed. We still believe in personal service, expert craftsmanship, and standing behind every product we sell. Three generations later, we're proud to carry on the tradition.</p>"
          }
        },
