            "content": "<p>Complimentary white-glove delivery and professional installation throughout the Puget Sound area. We handle everything so you don't have to.</p>"
          }
        },
        "service-2": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Recovering & Repairs",
            "heading_tag": "h4",
            "content": "<p>Breathe new life into your table with our professional recovering service. We also handle cushion replacement, slate leveling, and structural repairs.</p>"
